Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景學姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢  學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:22:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.89,0:23:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我吃一個好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不行啊  學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不塗些什麼的話  麵包會吸收蔬菜的水分變的黏乎乎的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被編織的  是悲傷的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  ef - a tale of memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「輪廓」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.17,0:23:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有不願意忘卻的回憶嗎？


